      "author": "Yan Tom",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107007608373039103575?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Target is newly opened. About 3 weeks ago. As of now, it's About 85% stocked. They have a grocery section. Not like an actual Supermarket, but close. You'll have most of your grocery shopping needs. Clean and a friendly staff.",
      "textTranslated": "Target baru saja dibuka, sekitar 3 minggu yang lalu. Saat ini, persediaannya sudah sekitar 85%. Mereka memiliki bagian bahan makanan. Tidak seperti supermarket sungguhan, tetapi hampir sama. Anda akan menemukan sebagian besar kebutuhan belanja bahan makanan Anda di sini. Bersih dan stafnya ramah.",
