    {
      "author": "Ali Marro",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104520003689997127514?hl=id",
      "rating": 1,
      "text": "Have had the absolute worst experiences at this target multiple times already since opening. They consistently only have one cashier for a line of 20 people long. The employees have no sense of responsibility and are constantly acting like “that’s not my job”. The cashier will not call over the manager to ask her to open more registers. In addition, they lock the shopping carts. God forbid you wanted to shop at both target and Whole Foods. My cart locked in the middle of the street in front of traffic with a cart full of $300+. I may have to go back to just shopping at East Hanover. Extremely disappointing",
      "textTranslated": "Saya sudah beberapa kali mengalami pengalaman terburuk di Target ini sejak dibuka. Mereka selalu hanya memiliki satu kasir untuk antrean sepanjang 20 orang. Para karyawan tidak memiliki rasa tanggung jawab dan selalu bertindak seolah-olah \"itu bukan pekerjaan saya\". Kasir tidak mau memanggil manajer untuk memintanya membuka lebih banyak kasir. Selain itu, mereka mengunci troli belanja. Celakanya, Anda ingin berbelanja di Target dan Whole Foods sekaligus. Troli saya terkunci di tengah jalan di depan lalu lintas dengan troli penuh berisi barang belanjaan senilai lebih dari $300. Saya mungkin harus kembali berbelanja di East Hanover saja. Sangat mengecewakan.",
      "date": "2026-04-06T15:52:12.316Z",
      "relativeDate": "seminggu lalu",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "responseFromOwner": null,
